    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>remaining peri peri spice mix</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong>, bring to the boil and cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>peri peri sauce</strong></p>",
